org.batfish.question.tracefilters

Class TraceFiltersQuestion

  • java.lang.Object
    • org.batfish.datamodel.questions.Question
      • org.batfish.datamodel.questions.IPacketTraceQuestion
        • org.batfish.question.tracefilters.TraceFiltersQuestion
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    IQuestion

    public class TraceFiltersQuestion
extends IPacketTraceQuestion
    Computes the fate of the flow at a filter. The set of filters to consider are controlled by node and filter regex fields. By default, all filters on all nodes are considered.
